Lanka Orix Leasing Advances After Quarterly Profit Surges

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-02-18T04:27:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/lanka-orix-leasing-advances-after-quarterly-profit-surges.html
Lanka Orix Leasing Plc. rose as much
as 6.2 percent in Colombo trading after reporting a third-
quarter profit of 718 million rupees, compared with 46 million
rupees a year earlier.  Colombo-based Lanka Orix was trading 1.9 percent higher at
139.2 rupees at 9:47 a.m. local time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
